layout print "/(ab,fn1)/(is5)/(irdata/gui/docpix/CaptureTheFlag.tga)"
paragraph "Rules:"
paragraph "Every player has one flag. It is your goal to steal the opponent’s flag and defend your own flag. When you steal the opponent’s flag, it needs to be carried to your own flag to win the round. If your own flag has been stolen in the meantime, you can’t score - it requires both flags to win!"
paragraph "In order to recapture your flag, it is sufficient to walk over the flag - then it will automatically be transported to its original position. First you might have to ‘persuade’ your opponent to drop it though..."

